me.description: I am a software professional who seeks to solve real word problems with the help of computers. My aim is to contribute in the creation of a globe enabled with technology and automation, thus help to save manual effort & time. I have worked and managed multiple areas of software engineering - From scratch or enhancing existing entities; & have a keen interest in learning new technologies. Currently, I am working as a Software Engineer at Narvar. I enjoy my work and try my best to contribute, both as an individual and as a team player.
me.headline: 8 Years of Experience || Presently at Narvar || Ex-DBS
